snippet.textDisplay:
Tip: go to the houses on the way to your destination because they can give you guns, medkits, and many more protection stuffs you can sell and use!‚ù§‚ù§

Tip 2: if you whistle you can signal other players or your friends where you are and they can follow the whistle (this works by them following your username that pops up when you whistle) when it turns night HIDE inside your base or any closed space. Collect food or supplies in the morning and design your base or house after. You can make a waypoint to your base or other places by clicking the random shapes under NIGHT ___ and click Waypoints. I recommend making the waypoint color a VERY BRIGHT color so you can find it easier. ONLY explore and find items in the DAYTIME or entities will find you. When its bloodmoon or when the store turns red that means its bloodmoon and DO NOT exit your base. The entities at bloodmoon will become faster and stronger. If its foggy, it means the same thing but they are only faster. Find tvs so your base can have light, if you keep clicking on and off on the tv it might play a channel with shows on it. But there is a very small chance you will get it. The arrows on the ground dont lead to anything its just like in normal shops where it shows you where the furnitures are but the arrows are overall NOT helpful. Make sure to keep your energy, hunger, and health up at ALL times. The sodas will NOT give you energy because its unhealthy. The foods I recommend are burgers, spaghetti, WATER, lemons, healthkits, ice cream, and many more aside from SODA. If you fall from a high place you can take health damage. Make sure to build a base as quick as you can when you join, but if its night time when you join you can find places with already built walls and use random stuff to block the entrance.
